# SSO Portal - Contoh Integrasi ke Aplikasi Lain
# Simpan file ini sebagai referensi cara mengintegrasikan aplikasi Anda ke SSO Portal

# ==========================================
# CARA KERJA SSO (FLOW)
# ==========================================
# 
# 1. User buka aplikasi Anda (misal: hrms.hqmedan.com)
# 2. Aplikasi cek apakah user sudah punya session
# 3. Jika belum, redirect ke SSO Portal:
#    -> https://portal.hqmedan.com/api/sso/authorize?app=hrms&redirect=https://hrms.hqmedan.com/sso/callback
# 4. SSO Portal login user (jika belum login)
# 5. SSO Portal generate one-time token, redirect ke callback URL:
#    -> https://hrms.hqmedan.com/sso/callback?sso_token=<TOKEN>
# 6. Aplikasi kirim POST ke SSO Portal untuk validasi token
# 7. SSO Portal return data user + JWT token
# 8. Aplikasi simpan session user

# ==========================================
# CONTOH: Node.js Express (Aplikasi Tujuan)
# ==========================================

SSO_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-dari-admin-panel
SSO_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-dari-admin-panel
SSO_PORTAL_URL=https://portal.hqmedan.com

# Endpoint di aplikasi Anda:
# GET /sso/callback?sso_token=xxx
# -> Validasi token ke portal, buat session lokal

